Global Cordless Band Saw Market Insights
Cordless Band Saw Market size was valued at USD 0.67 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 1.14 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 7.0% from 2024 to 2030.

Cordless Band Saw Market Overview
The cordless band saw market has witnessed substantial growth, driven by the increasing demand for portable and efficient tools in various industries such as construction, automotive, and DIY applications. The market size was valued at approximately USD 1.7 billion in 2023 and is expected to expand at a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of around 6.5% from 2024 to 2030. This growth is attributed to advancements in battery technology, improved efficiency, and the rising trend of cordless power tools that offer convenience and flexibility. The market's expansion is also bolstered by growing consumer interest in tools that deliver high performance with ease of use, and the increasing adoption of cordless equipment for professional and home-based tasks. In addition, manufacturers are focusing on enhancing the cutting power and battery life of cordless band saws, thus further fueling their popularity across various end-user industries.

